On Mon, 23 Jan 2012, Pete O wrote:

> Thanks for the response, David.  Always wondered why the mods were so
> uptight on that rule when memory gets less expensive by the day.  One
> disadvantage of having all the text cut out from the previous email is if
> one needs a reference point, you have to go back and open up the one you
